data.name: tagSearchTextBox.ToolTip
data.value:
Search for a specific tag. The length that the search begins can be changed in the settings.
Enter - Toggle the top search result on/off. Enter when empty - Save the file. Left / Right - (If textbox is empty) Go to previous/next file. ALT + Left / Right - Skip backwards/forwards through playing video. Down / Up - Move down/up to highlight tags (Simulates Tab/Shift+Tab). CTRL + D - Delete the current file (Requires confirmation). CTRL + P - Reload the tags used on the last saved image. CTRL + S - Save the file. CTRL + Z - Undo. CTRL + Y - Redo.
